22/01/2008
TIRANA, Albania -- At its first plenary session of the year on Monday (January 21st), parliament unanimously approved a draft resolution proposed by the opposition Socialist Party that pledges commitment from all parties to accomplish the judicial and electoral reforms needed for NATO integration. 
Albania hopes to receive an invitation for membership in April. 
(GazetaShqiptare, Shqip, Korrieri, Standard - 22/01/08; Balkanweb, Top-Channel, Albanian prime minister website - 21/01/08)
